    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="要如何显示或取消小说本文中所显示的下划线（设定资料链接）？" class="article-title">
          要如何显示或取消小说本文中所显示的下划线（设定资料链接）？
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>可于小说作品详细页面的格式设置切换设定资料链接。</p>
<p>■设定资料链接是什么？<br>这是可供读者在阅读小说作品时参考设定资料的功能。<br>正文中登录有设定资料的单词会显示下划线，点选则会显示其说明内容。</p>
<p>▶<a href="#h_01FM6GZKZ2JVWKFMSZQ59VTP9A" target="_self">电脑版</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM6GZV7XZRB09N6KJNQ40NB6" target="_self">手机版</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM6H02MH6QV8HACVQ05QQ7S0" target="_self">APP版</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6GZKZ2JVWKFMSZQ59VTP9A">电脑版</h3>
<p>可由小说本文下方的「Aa」切换显示或取消设定资料链接。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330933401/03________________01.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330933401/03________________01.png" alt="03________________01.png" width="544" height="637"></a></p>
<p>设为显示时，已登录设定资料的单词将会显示下划线，用户可快速确认详细信息。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330937113/03________________02.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330937113/03________________02.png" alt="03________________02.png" width="550" height="425"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6GZV7XZRB09N6KJNQ40NB6">手机版</h3>
<p>可由小说正文上方的「・・・」切换显示或取消「设定资料链接」。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409338756889/03______________01.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409338756889/03______________01.png" alt="03______________01.png" width="566" height="534"></a></p>
<p>链接会以下列形式显示。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409330957849/03______________02.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409330957849/03______________02.png" alt="03______________02.png" width="568" height="931"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM6H02MH6QV8HACVQ05QQ7S0">APP版</h3>
<p>目前APP版尚不支持切换「设定资料链接」功能。</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
